content:
✨WELCOME TO OUR ONLINE ENGAGEMENT COMMUNITY✨

In this space, we will be taking action in a number of ways to engage supporters and voters online. From combatting misinformation, connecting with our own online communities, and amplifying campaign messaging during key moments, we will leverage online spaces to inform and reach voters.

Help us sort you into the proper channels! React here with the following emojis, depending on the type of action you want to take:

React with 🗣️ if you want to amplify Team Harris messaging

React with 💻 if you want to connect with your online community

React with 🐣 if you want to participate in the Twitter Community Notes Program. 

React with 🔊 if you want to take action on TikTok

React with 👾 if you want to take action on Reddit

Make sure you join Reach here: https://app.reach.vote/join/7DRDMN  to get access to campaign content to share with your online communities!
